# AI CAR

ESP32-based smart car controlled over WiFi using JSON commands.

## Features

- WiFi-controlled ESP32 car
- HTTP API for sending commands
- Queue-based motion system
- Independent drive + steering control
- Supports single commands + sequences

## How?

The ESP32 hosts a local server and listens for JSON commands.

Each command controls:
- drive (forward/backward)
- steer (left/right)
- duration for both

Commands are queued and executed one by one.


